title: IS_STREAMING_FILE_READY
content:
0xA194934D// IsStreamingFileReady
BOOL IS_STREAMING_FILE_READY(char* registerAs);Parameters:registerAs: The file name to check, for example asset.ydr.Returns: Whether or not the streaming file has been registered.Experimental: This native may be altered or removed in future versions of CitizenFX without warning.Returns whether an asynchronous streaming file registration completed.
